--------------------------------------------------------------------

The raft-config project provides raft-config configuration tool.

Features:
=========

Native Build using make directly:
================
Configure only:
==============
~/RAFT/build$\
 export SRCDIR=$PWD/../raft-config;\
 export BUILDIR=$PWD;\
 export PREFIX=usr;\
 make -C $BUILDIR -f $SRCDIR/conf.mk conf

Compile only:
============
~/RAFT/build$ make all

Installation:
============
~/RAFT/build$\
 export DESTDIR=$PWD/install;\
 make install

Native Build using U2UP (out-of-source-build):
=============================================
Do everything (including the u2up package):
==========================================
~$ cd RAFT/build
~/RAFT/build$ ../raft-config/u2up/u2up-build.sh -b ./ ../raft-config/ -p usr -d tmp

or wthout having build directory prepared:
-----------------------------------------
~/RAFT$ raft-config/u2up/u2up-build.sh -b build raft-config/ -p usr -d build/install

Configure only:
==============
~/RAFT/build$ ../raft-config/u2up/u2up-build.sh -b ./ ../raft-config/ -p usr --conf

Compile only:
============
~/RAFT/build$ ../raft-config/u2up/u2up-build.sh -b ./ ../raft-config/ -p usr --make

Installation:
============
~/RAFT/build$ ../raft-config/u2up/u2up-build.sh -b ./ ../raft-config/ -p usr -d tmp --inst

Cleaning:
========
rm -rf ~/RAFT/build

U2UP packaging:
==============
~/RAFT/build$ ./raft_config-0.1.2.u2up [name | version | required | list | extract]

